<title>
Accessory Drive Belt Inspection
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
There is a risk of personal injury if the service work described below is performed while the engine is running.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Make sure that the ENGINE IS NOT RUNNING before performing the service work described below.
</ptxt>
</attention1>
<ptxt>
Inspect belt for cracks, cuts, deformation, wear and contamination. If any defect is found, replace belt.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Check belt for tension.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
